title: DONKEY: Oil Protesters Arrested After Throwing Tomato Soup at Van Gogh Painting
itunes:title: DONKEY: Oil Protesters Arrested After Throwing Tomato Soup at Van Gogh Painting
description:
Charlamagne gives "Donkey of the Day" to "Just Stop Oil" activists for throwing tomato soup on Vincent Van Gogh’s famous “Sunflowers” painting.
